data.description:
Welcome to your next project in Mandarin! This charming home with two bedrooms and two bathrooms is a canvas for your dream transformation. Enjoy a living space downstairs off the kitchen with a fireplace & vaulted ceiling.  A sunroom overlooking the spacious yard with pond views is just off the living room.
The downstairs bedroom has a bathroom in need of some TLC, offering you the opportunity to customize it as you like. Upstairs, the primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom, also ready for your personal touch. The additional loft area is perfect for a cozy reading nook or home office. .  This home is on  a quiet cul-de-sac & there's a pickleball court in the neighborhood to enjoy with friends and neighbors! Selling as-is in a great location. Unleash your creativity and turn this opportunity into your dream home!
